Yara Goubran (n'asụsụ Arabic يارا جبران), amụrụ n'abalị iri na abụọ n'ọnwa Eprel bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri nke Egypt nke a ma ama maka ọrụ ya na ihe nkiri Egypt nke onwe ya yana ọrụ ya na fim Basra na-enweta ihe nrite na ọrụ Nahla
Goubran gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum America nke Cairo ebe ọ gụrụ mgbasa ozi na ihe nkiri
Na mgbakwunye na Basra, ọ pụtakwara na ihe nkiri Egypt Karim's Harem (Hareem Kareem) na Farsh w ghata na usoro telivishọn Egypt Lahazaat hariga na Arfat al bahr.
